{"tid":1970151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰維斯：訓練絕不可能比C.朗拿度早到 提前3小時他都在","createTime":"2020-04-13T02:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T19:36:18.000Z","uid":25345,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9b80c6e95c25a6a459f1232f2bd20290b786bdf7","tid":1970151,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"泰維斯：這還是人嗎<br />\n<br />\n  阿根廷球星泰維斯透露，他曾經嘗試過提前一小時，一個半小時乃至三個小時去訓練，然而每次他都看到C.朗拿度已經在那裡了。<br />\n<br />\n  「我記得在C.朗拿度身上發生的事情，就像世界上所有女人肯定都會看到的那樣：他幾乎所有時間都花在健身房裡，對此他真的有一種癡迷。」泰維斯對《馬卡報》表示。<br />\n<br />\n  「如果我們早上9點訓練，然後我決定8點鍾提前到，他就已經在那裡了。我7點半到，他也在那裡。那我就說，難道比這傢伙更早來是不可能的嗎？有一天我決定早上6點鍾到，然後發現他已經在那兒了。半睡半醒的，但在那裡。」"},{"pid":"53827f10e9e775a32911b9994b4bf874885fa8ad","tid":1970151,"uid":261873,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"想知佢個仔第二時會畀佢操成點"},{"pid":"4ed80c806f7b6a3c30afff1fd589025e92aa4e94","tid":1970151,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/03/17/10/324731D200000578-0-image-m-36_1458209427703.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F03%2F17%2F10%2F324731D200000578-0-image-m-36_1458209427703.jpg&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=6af36a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/03/17/10/324731D200000578-0-image-m-36_1458209427703.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"50beccc41d24967c284c69066b0167f329fc97e9","tid":1970151,"uid":213217,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"53827f10e9e775a32911b9994b4bf874885fa8ad","tid":1970151,"uid":261873,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"想知佢個仔第二時會畀佢操成點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:07:25.000Z","msg":"已經屈緊同年機，場場入幾球"},{"pid":"d10f0727f47f5258aca93c3bd23dd92a1c2809d0","tid":1970151,"uid":120070,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:1